{"tid":1317282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"制高點其實有好多野玩","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:54:18.000Z","uid":225569,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1228308bffb0e76f47eac9fc3eb6805b07af59","tid":1317282,"uid":225569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"發夢嗰時我通常都唔敢行最快走到最前<br />\n我自己比較鍾意企响高啲嘅地方望下面拍野影野<br />\n突然間覺得急屎又急尿，忍唔住就打算想搵啲薄薄地嘅膠袋裝住先<br />\n發夢有左咁多次經驗，你都知啲獅子狗好少會自己一條响地下嘛，群埋一齊<br />\n生平最憎食獅子狗，又有制高點，仲唔一包包車落去？<br />\n夠多嘅話成桶淋都得呀<br />\nbtw係驚整到啲反光背心朋友啫<br />\n啲獅子狗變晒做咖哩味，仲唔拿拿聲撤退翻去沖涼咩<br />\n我就唔撚信佢仲企响度唔走呀"},{"pid":"f4f53a9dbb169cbeab3c4161887d466ab4d95116","tid":1317282,"uid":199902,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:13:06.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩......<br />\n易TK之餘<br />\n仲會有漬留低 又跣又臭<br />\n應該有其他嘢好玩啲"},{"pid":"b81e82b94284b292f3182b7064fe7461d2578001","tid":1317282,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:13:57.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"c0e30284f1a7dc2e6f3a06d3ac9b34b001e30041","tid":1317282,"uid":209367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:14:11.000Z","msg":"有dna...."},{"pid":"e15803ea929395c4de87bf9780274cd2c038d501","tid":1317282,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:14:34.000Z","msg":"顏料"},{"pid":"af8a51af700e036f707ff0139e32890c53839d37","tid":1317282,"uid":62776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"丫叉，波子，水彈<br />\n波子仲可以一邊徹一邊放地下<br />\n阻一阻班狗沖上黎<br />\n但驚TK到記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39393a647f6d8a83fccc54723768ba683abc6a20","tid":1317282,"uid":49695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"唔好玩屎"},{"pid":"7c5ddaada3eea71888f6e0d99e76f52ec7639d5b","tid":1317282,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39393a647f6d8a83fccc54723768ba683abc6a20","tid":1317282,"uid":49695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"唔好玩屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"咁玩狗屎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d101bde0f8cf6177ea671130970c6c398c09d2f2","tid":1317282,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:54:18.000Z","msg":"硬物&gt;掉完會留番係原地，之後可以繼續掉<br />\n<br />\n屎&gt;會留低臭味係原地，兄弟們既口罩冇班狗咁高級，會因為惡臭而唔肯留守<br />\n<br />\n請三思"}]}